WEBVTT

01:47.148 --> 01:48.733
The situation is complicated,

01:48.817 --> 01:51.069
but what we need to do hasn’t changed.

01:51.152 --> 01:54.030
First, obtain the elixir.

01:54.114 --> 01:56.241
Second, survive and leave the island.

01:57.158 --> 01:59.828
For now, let’s confirm only
the information we need.

01:59.911 --> 02:02.997
We won’t worry about
the island’s mysteries at this point.

02:03.081 --> 02:04.582
What matters most

02:04.666 --> 02:06.626
is how to escape the island.

02:06.709 --> 02:08.628
So, what’s the plan?

02:08.711 --> 02:11.339
Mei knows the method.

02:16.636 --> 02:17.846
I see.

02:19.222 --> 02:21.224
Horai is a vast fortress,

02:21.891 --> 02:25.145
modeled after the China’s Epang Palace.

02:25.228 --> 02:27.188
It was built to complete the elixir

02:27.272 --> 02:29.899
and welcome
the First Emperor to the island.

02:29.983 --> 02:33.528
In other words, entering and leaving
the island itself isn’t impossible.

02:33.611 --> 02:36.823
However, there are monsters
in the surrounding sea.

02:36.906 --> 02:40.535
They serve as sentries, preventing
the island’s creatures from leaving.

02:41.870 --> 02:43.288
Like that huge one I saw.

02:43.872 --> 02:46.875
Compared to the Tensen,
aren’t they less dangerous?

02:46.958 --> 02:51.045
Humans can’t compete with sea beasts,
and in a small boat at that.

02:51.129 --> 02:54.549
Neither killing them
nor escaping is possible,

02:55.133 --> 02:56.551
no matter how skilled a swordsman you are.

02:58.636 --> 03:02.932
To begin with, the assumption
is that we don’t fight the Tensen.

03:03.016 --> 03:06.144
We swiftly steal the elixir
without being noticed

03:06.227 --> 03:07.562
and leave the island by ship.

03:07.645 --> 03:10.940
The goal is solely to escape the island.

03:11.024 --> 03:13.610
There are ships
and floodgates beneath Horai,

03:13.693 --> 03:16.321
and the monsters are said to be trained

03:16.404 --> 03:18.531
not to attack ships
that depart from there.

03:20.241 --> 03:24.579
Floodgates...
That presence I felt near the shore?

03:25.204 --> 03:27.457
Do you know where the elixir is?

03:28.458 --> 03:30.835
Probably.

03:31.920 --> 03:36.841
In the laboratory I shared with Rien.

03:38.134 --> 03:39.677
Either way,

03:39.761 --> 03:42.263
the route passes right
through enemy territory.

03:42.764 --> 03:45.808
We don’t have much time, but I want
to prepare as much as possible.

03:45.892 --> 03:48.186
That’s why Gabimaru and Yuzuriha will...

03:48.978 --> 03:50.688
teach us stealth techniques.

03:50.772 --> 03:52.190
Huh? Me?

03:54.025 --> 03:55.944
What, seduction tactics?

03:56.945 --> 03:58.655
No. I'm talking about Tao.

04:02.242 --> 04:03.326
All right, first...

04:04.452 --> 04:08.706
I’ll teach you a technique to dilute
your Tao for substitution techniques.

04:09.290 --> 04:10.333
What for?

04:10.416 --> 04:11.834
Give back Sen-chan’s keepsake!

04:11.918 --> 04:13.920
Now, now, my students.

04:14.003 --> 04:17.090
Nothing beats seeing for yourself. Watch.

04:21.344 --> 04:22.303
KAWARIMI

04:22.387 --> 04:25.056
See? If you talk, it’s over.

04:25.139 --> 04:28.768
Diluting Tao is the same
as thinning your very existence.

04:29.352 --> 04:31.354
It even worked on the Tensen.

04:31.437 --> 04:33.815
Perfect for infiltration, right?

04:33.898 --> 04:37.443
All right, everyone,
deep breaths and focus.

04:39.654 --> 04:40.780
Ow!

04:41.489 --> 04:44.367
- What are you doing?
- Your Tao is disturbed.

04:45.243 --> 04:47.954
No matter what happens,
keep your mind calm.

04:51.124 --> 04:54.252
Tao is surprisingly physical.

04:54.335 --> 04:57.297
Like sumo or jujutsu,
you can redirect force

04:57.380 --> 04:59.632
and even use your opponent’s Tao.

05:00.216 --> 05:03.011
I’ve also thought of certain
countermeasures based on attributes.

05:03.094 --> 05:05.305
To begin with, in martial arts,
fa jin and Tao are...

05:05.388 --> 05:07.682
He's pretty theory-heavy, isn't he?

05:07.765 --> 05:09.350
- Maybe he's a nerd?
- ...there's a high chance you can do it...

05:09.851 --> 05:12.437
Now then, first dislocate the neck bones...

05:12.520 --> 05:13.354
You think we can do that?!

05:15.189 --> 05:16.983
Those who can’t do it die first.

05:17.775 --> 05:19.360
That’s how it was in village training.

05:20.945 --> 05:23.114
All right, focus, focus.

05:23.698 --> 05:25.616
No matter what’s done to you, don’t react.

05:25.700 --> 05:28.870
Relax by dislocating
every bone in your body.

05:28.953 --> 05:31.122
Don’t react, don’t react.

05:31.205 --> 05:33.750
Stop your heart without dying.

05:38.421 --> 05:41.049
How the hell do you guys not get tired?

05:41.132 --> 05:43.426
If you handle Tao well,
fatigue is minimal.

05:44.427 --> 05:46.637
Why can you suddenly use it so well?

05:47.305 --> 05:48.890
Who knows. Talent?

05:51.267 --> 05:55.146
Since it happened, I feel like
something about my senses changed...

06:00.943 --> 06:04.238
From where you stand now,
I could probably take you down easily.

06:04.947 --> 06:07.950
Oh? Really?

06:08.034 --> 06:09.869
You’ve got some nerve, man-woman.

06:09.952 --> 06:11.579
It’s strange.

06:12.080 --> 06:15.291
We started out on opposing sides,

06:15.374 --> 06:18.503
yet now we’re cooperating
toward the same goal.

06:19.629 --> 06:21.047
And that I can find myself...

06:21.631 --> 06:24.092
wishing that no one here will die.

06:24.175 --> 06:28.638
If you can’t take me down, I’m putting you
in a Chinese dress too, man-woman.

06:28.721 --> 06:29.847
Want to die?

06:29.931 --> 06:30.765
The same...

06:30.848 --> 06:32.100
Interesting. Think you can do it?

06:32.183 --> 06:33.392
You?

06:33.476 --> 06:34.936
- If you can, then try.
- Wait, wait.

06:35.019 --> 06:35.853
Huh?

06:35.937 --> 06:38.064
Let’s decide the teams first.

06:39.357 --> 06:41.109
Kenryu, stand over there.

06:41.192 --> 06:43.111
Huh? Don’t order me around!

06:43.194 --> 06:45.071
Stop resisting!

06:45.154 --> 06:46.739
Gabimaru, you too.

06:47.573 --> 06:49.534
Yuzuriha and Toma, over there.

06:49.617 --> 06:50.993
Okay, okay.

06:52.161 --> 06:54.288
Lovely braids, young lady.

06:54.372 --> 06:55.289
I’ll kill you.

06:55.373 --> 06:56.541
Fuchi.

06:57.416 --> 06:58.543
Mei.

06:59.210 --> 07:01.546
In case we encounter a Tensen,

07:01.629 --> 07:04.173
let’s understand our own Tao attributes.

07:04.257 --> 07:07.218
Sagiri has the same wood attribute as me.

07:08.261 --> 07:09.679
Gabimaru and Kenryu are fire.

07:11.764 --> 07:14.934
And water, metal, and earth.

07:15.017 --> 07:17.770
These attributes influence one another.

07:20.022 --> 07:22.442
MUTUAL GENERATION

07:22.525 --> 07:24.444
MUTUAL OVERCOMING

07:24.527 --> 07:25.403
MUTUAL OVERCOMING
MUTUAL GENERATION

07:25.486 --> 07:28.489
Strengthening another’s Tao
is called mutual generation.

07:28.573 --> 07:31.075
Weakening it, on the other hand,
is called mutual overcoming.

07:31.159 --> 07:34.203
Do you know the Tensen's attributes too?

07:34.287 --> 07:36.581
I do...

07:38.708 --> 07:40.168
I remember.

07:40.251 --> 07:44.672
Ju Fa, fire. Tao Fa, wood.

07:44.755 --> 07:47.425
Zhu Jin, Ran, water.

07:47.508 --> 07:52.180
Gui Fa, metal. Mu Dan, Rien, earth.

07:52.263 --> 07:55.308
If your attribute restrains the enemy’s,
your techniques will work.

07:56.184 --> 08:00.438
However, if it’s the opposite...
you have no chance.

08:01.147 --> 08:04.066
Abandon everything... and run.

08:07.945 --> 08:10.198
The teams were decided
based on compatibility.

08:10.281 --> 08:14.160
One to secure the escape route
and one to seize the elixir.

08:14.827 --> 08:17.955
The elixir team needs speed and stealth.

08:18.539 --> 08:19.540
Only those who can use Tao.

08:19.624 --> 08:20.666
- What?
- A small number is better.

08:20.750 --> 08:22.210
Hey, are you serious?

08:22.293 --> 08:25.588
- The elixir team is way more dangerous!
- No objections.

08:26.172 --> 08:29.258
The escape team must secure
the ship underground

08:29.342 --> 08:31.344
and open the floodgates.

08:31.427 --> 08:35.306
Three people for each
of the three roles makes sense.

08:36.682 --> 08:38.434
- Sensei.
- Hm?

08:38.518 --> 08:39.435
I just...

08:39.519 --> 08:40.978
Um...

08:41.062 --> 08:43.314
It’s all right, Nurugai.

08:44.440 --> 08:45.900
I haven’t forgotten.

08:47.360 --> 08:48.236
Yeah...

08:50.238 --> 08:52.323
From what that bonsai guy said...

08:52.406 --> 08:53.533
Not bonsai.

08:54.116 --> 08:56.035
You want to leave
the island too, don’t you, miss?

08:59.121 --> 09:02.458
Then we could just
let her leave on her own

09:02.542 --> 09:05.294
without waiting
for the elixir team, couldn't we?

09:05.378 --> 09:06.671
- Wait.
- Huh?

09:08.172 --> 09:10.299
Are you really okay with this?

09:11.425 --> 09:12.969
Oh! Gabi!

09:13.052 --> 09:16.722
That's right. The elixir team
is dangerous, isn't it?

09:18.474 --> 09:21.894
Do you wish to just leave
the island like this?

09:23.479 --> 09:26.607
Isn’t there something you’d regret
before leaving the island?

09:27.191 --> 09:29.944
You could have escaped on your own.

09:31.320 --> 09:32.947
But you didn’t.

09:35.449 --> 09:37.577
I couldn’t hear everything last time.

09:37.660 --> 09:39.704
Let me hear it now.

09:44.166 --> 09:45.835
I’ll translate.

09:48.212 --> 09:50.423
I...

09:50.506 --> 09:54.844
think it's bad what Rien is doing.

09:54.927 --> 09:57.513
He's killed so, so many people.

09:58.598 --> 10:02.351
Why didn’t Master Xu Fu stop it?

10:02.435 --> 10:05.730
I want to leave the island quickly.
Everything is scary.

10:07.064 --> 10:10.359
But! Just once more...

10:10.443 --> 10:13.779
I want to see Rien and the Master.

10:14.739 --> 10:17.867
I want to ask why they changed.

10:17.950 --> 10:21.287
Long ago, the two of them were kind.

10:21.370 --> 10:23.247
They were kind, and yet...

10:26.042 --> 10:29.795
Risking danger just to talk to the Tensen...

10:29.879 --> 10:31.505
What will you do after that?

10:33.090 --> 10:34.258
And then...

10:34.842 --> 10:37.970
And then I'll leave the island

10:38.888 --> 10:40.389
and live a normal life.

10:43.476 --> 10:45.561
Let’s protect what’s normal.

10:46.145 --> 10:48.814
Peacefully, properly.

10:49.857 --> 10:51.442
I know it’s dangerous.

10:51.942 --> 10:54.362
But just seeing them is enough.

10:54.945 --> 10:55.863
I miss them.

10:59.450 --> 11:00.993
Then let’s go.

11:01.744 --> 11:03.913
If you just want to see them,
it might be possible.

11:03.996 --> 11:04.914
But...

11:04.997 --> 11:09.293
Otherwise, your "normal" life
can’t begin, can it?

11:10.961 --> 11:14.924
Leave the journey to me.
I will get you to your destination.

11:18.052 --> 11:18.969
Okay!

11:22.932 --> 11:25.393
With this,
the "Rite of Ascension" is over.

11:28.646 --> 11:32.650
So? Big fancy ritual,
but does it mean anything?

11:32.733 --> 11:34.193
Who knows?

11:34.276 --> 11:36.404
It’s an old custom.

11:36.487 --> 11:38.155
Newly born Doshi,

11:38.739 --> 11:42.284
or anyone permitted
into the castle, everyone does it.

11:43.577 --> 11:46.038
This feels better after all.

11:46.122 --> 11:48.624
All right, let’s reintroduce ourselves.

11:48.707 --> 11:50.835
- I'm Tao--
- Don't give your name.

11:51.335 --> 11:53.879
There’s no value in that
when dealing with livestock.

11:54.463 --> 11:56.757
Just being in the same room makes me sick.

11:57.633 --> 11:59.760
Agreed, you weed.

12:07.017 --> 12:09.812
You should’ve killed me back then.

12:10.438 --> 12:11.897
Now I can see it.

12:12.481 --> 12:13.941
Your movements.

12:14.525 --> 12:15.860
Stop.

12:15.943 --> 12:19.738
That man is my research subject
and my guest.

12:19.822 --> 12:22.241
I won’t allow you to harm him.

12:22.324 --> 12:24.994
Come with me, Chobe.

12:26.370 --> 12:27.997
Where are we going?

12:28.080 --> 12:30.708
To examine your Tao in detail.

12:31.333 --> 12:33.919
This place is pretty complicated.

12:34.003 --> 12:35.880
Feng shui design.

12:35.963 --> 12:38.090
It follows Tao singularities
called dragon veins

12:38.174 --> 12:40.634
and their pathways, "dragon arteries,"

12:40.718 --> 12:42.511
expanded and renovated accordingly.

12:44.054 --> 12:48.517
You’ll understand eventually.
You have talent for Tao.

12:50.060 --> 12:51.270
That guy earlier...

12:51.854 --> 12:54.565
Before, I was no match for him.

12:55.191 --> 12:56.901
But now, it’s different.

12:57.902 --> 13:01.447
I've clearly adapted. My power is growing.

13:02.781 --> 13:07.036
That’s why I can tell how dangerous
this one in front of me is.

13:07.119 --> 13:09.205
He’s on a different level
from the other Tensen.

13:09.955 --> 13:12.500
I need to find more of their weaknesses.

13:12.583 --> 13:14.418
As things stand, I have no chance.

13:15.419 --> 13:17.087
As things stand...

13:19.089 --> 13:21.550
This is my laboratory.

13:31.101 --> 13:33.145
What is that?

13:33.229 --> 13:35.189
An external elixir flower, Pangu.

13:36.023 --> 13:40.069
Elixirs are extracted Tao
from humans transformed into flowers,

13:40.152 --> 13:43.447
but the amount
from one person is negligible.

13:43.531 --> 13:45.616
With Pangu, however,

13:45.699 --> 13:47.701
you can generate many elixirs at once.

13:51.914 --> 13:54.959
But elixirs are hard to preserve.

13:55.042 --> 13:56.794
Over time, the flower’s Tao

13:56.877 --> 13:59.838
completely consumes the human Tao.

13:59.922 --> 14:02.424
This Pangu will eventually wither too.

14:02.925 --> 14:06.512
Before reaching the quality
and quantity I desire.

14:07.012 --> 14:10.182
That’s why I want your rare Tao.

14:10.266 --> 14:11.850
Give me your cooperation.

14:13.060 --> 14:16.564
A large supply of elixirs...
for what purpose?

14:18.774 --> 14:21.277
Is he planning to turn Toma into this?

14:21.360 --> 14:24.238
That’s it. That surge of Tao.

14:25.030 --> 14:27.366
I’ve seen many humans before,

14:27.449 --> 14:29.577
but none with a Tao like yours.

14:29.660 --> 14:31.537
Beautiful...

14:32.037 --> 14:36.041
Don’t worry. It’s only research.

14:36.542 --> 14:38.711
I won’t kill you.

14:39.295 --> 14:41.463
I’ll just use a part of you.

14:41.547 --> 14:43.549
If it regenerates, there’s no problem.

14:44.049 --> 14:47.094
Of course, I'll also
have you train your Tao.

14:47.177 --> 14:50.472
It’ll lead to better research results.

14:56.103 --> 14:57.730
That's just what I was hoping for.

15:17.082 --> 15:18.250
You're joking, right?

15:18.834 --> 15:22.379
You want to sneak in tonight?
Come on, it's time for bed.

15:23.047 --> 15:25.507
Timing your move
is basic shinobi practice.

15:25.591 --> 15:28.886
Unlike you, I’m human.

15:29.386 --> 15:31.138
I think it’s good.

15:31.722 --> 15:34.308
At night, when the flowers close,

15:34.391 --> 15:37.394
is the time when our Tao is weakest.

15:37.478 --> 15:38.687
Well...

15:38.771 --> 15:42.316
It’s better to act before
the new arrivals catch up.

15:42.399 --> 15:44.693
We’ve rested relatively well.

15:44.777 --> 15:46.862
I’m fine with it.

15:46.946 --> 15:50.324
Me too. I want to leave
the island as soon as possible.

15:50.908 --> 15:52.701
Fatigue doesn’t matter.

15:56.330 --> 15:58.791
I don’t want to keep her
waiting any longer.

16:00.167 --> 16:02.586
We’ll go ahead and prepare the way.

16:09.510 --> 16:11.929
Once we get a look
at the situation, we’ll signal.

16:12.554 --> 16:15.683
Red fire means abort. Blue fire means...

16:19.436 --> 16:20.437
Continue as planned.

16:21.605 --> 16:22.564
Let’s go.

16:23.565 --> 16:25.401
So, this is the end then.

16:25.484 --> 16:28.821
You knew from the start
it wouldn’t take long.

16:29.780 --> 16:31.615
Tonight, we leave the island.

16:34.159 --> 16:38.455
Horai is divided
into an inner and outer castle.

16:38.539 --> 16:41.083
We fought Mu Dan in the outer castle.

16:41.166 --> 16:45.379
The inner castle contains
multiple Tensen palaces.

16:45.462 --> 16:49.591
Each Tensen residence
corresponds to their training.

16:50.259 --> 16:51.427
Bochu Palace,

16:51.510 --> 16:55.597
where Ju Fa and Tao Fa pursue
immortality through union.

16:55.681 --> 16:57.182
The Taisoku Palace,

16:57.266 --> 17:00.978
where Zhu Jin seeks
immortality through breathing.

17:01.061 --> 17:02.604
The Douin Palace,

17:02.688 --> 17:05.858
where Ran seeks immortality
through physical exercises.

17:05.941 --> 17:07.443
The Shuitsu Palace,

17:07.526 --> 17:10.863
where Gui Fa seeks
immortality through meditation.

17:10.946 --> 17:12.698
The Shuten Palace,

17:12.781 --> 17:16.869
where Mu Dan seeks immortality
through Tao of organs and pressure points.

17:16.952 --> 17:18.078
So, in other words,

17:18.162 --> 17:21.874
each immortal specializes
in their own research?

17:22.458 --> 17:24.001
They teach one another.

17:24.084 --> 17:25.669
I see.

17:26.420 --> 17:27.504
I see.

17:27.588 --> 17:31.508
And the elixir is in the Ren Tan Palace,

17:32.342 --> 17:34.219
Rien's laboratory.

17:36.221 --> 17:39.016
But at night, Rien isn’t there.

17:40.142 --> 17:44.563
The external elixir flowers wilt at night,
so she can't do research.

17:45.105 --> 17:48.025
At night, Rien is in the main palace,

17:48.108 --> 17:50.527
Master Xu Fu’s castle.

17:50.611 --> 17:52.821
One key point.

17:52.905 --> 17:55.532
Do not engage the Tensen.

17:55.616 --> 17:58.160
If you do, the plan fails.

17:58.243 --> 18:01.038
Thieving at night has its problems.

18:01.121 --> 18:04.124
Moonlight doesn’t reach
deep inside large estates.

18:04.208 --> 18:07.711
Knowing the internal layout
in advance is essential.

18:08.337 --> 18:12.174
But the Tensen castles
are constantly being renovated, right?

18:13.217 --> 18:17.096
Not knowing and not seeing,
that’s impossible for a heist.

18:17.179 --> 18:20.224
No. That’s exactly why this team
was chosen, wasn't it?

18:20.307 --> 18:21.433
Gabimaru.

18:21.934 --> 18:25.020
That's right. See with Tao, not your eyes.

18:27.189 --> 18:29.066
Inorganic Tao is weak,
but if you sense it,

18:29.149 --> 18:31.193
you can understand the structure.

18:31.276 --> 18:34.446
That’s why we've chosen people
skilled in Tao perception.

18:34.530 --> 18:36.824
If humans are the materials for elixirs,

18:36.907 --> 18:39.701
then the lab should have many corpses.

18:39.785 --> 18:42.121
The place where that Tao is strongest

18:42.204 --> 18:44.081
is the Ren Tan Palace.

18:50.045 --> 18:52.214
If it disturbs your Tao, no need to look.

18:53.549 --> 18:55.843
I’m fine. I’m used to it.

18:56.927 --> 18:58.554
I'm fine too.

18:59.138 --> 19:00.806
This calmness...

19:01.390 --> 19:02.891
This is a shinobi.

19:03.892 --> 19:07.646
Following Yuzuriha, if we dilute
our Tao while moving through the castle,

19:08.230 --> 19:09.648
even the guards won’t notice.

19:11.859 --> 19:13.610
And when eliminating someone...

19:29.585 --> 19:32.546
If it’s instantaneous,
no one around will notice.

19:37.551 --> 19:39.219
Incredible efficiency...

19:40.554 --> 19:42.598
In just a few hours...

19:42.681 --> 19:45.058
we’ll be on a ship, leaving the island!

19:47.561 --> 19:50.022
The elixir should be in here.

19:51.106 --> 19:53.066
I don't sense any Tensen.

19:59.781 --> 20:03.535
Simple structure, sparse layout.

20:19.676 --> 20:21.678
Dilute Tao and hide.

20:22.346 --> 20:24.056
We’re thinking the same thing.

20:25.515 --> 20:27.184
R-Ran!

20:29.478 --> 20:32.439
So they've been under
your guidance after all, sister.

20:33.690 --> 20:35.567
You seem well.

20:36.151 --> 20:37.569
Why...

20:37.653 --> 20:40.572
We received information
from a certain man.

20:42.908 --> 20:44.868
About 20 landed.

20:44.952 --> 20:47.204
Half of them have special abilities.

20:47.287 --> 20:48.622
In other words,

20:48.705 --> 20:52.334
they possess Tao
of quality comparable to his.

20:52.417 --> 20:56.296
Did he break under research
and give up his comrades?

20:56.380 --> 20:57.923
No.

20:59.216 --> 21:01.551
They’re not comrades. They’re enemies.

21:01.635 --> 21:05.806
Amazing! You've kept your sanity
after Rien's "research"!

21:05.889 --> 21:08.517
They’re still lurking nearby.

21:08.600 --> 21:10.852
They probably plan
on making their way here.

21:10.936 --> 21:11.937
How do you know?

21:12.020 --> 21:16.191
I can feel my younger brother's Tao
among them.

21:16.275 --> 21:19.945
After injuring Toma,
it became even clearer.

21:20.028 --> 21:22.948
They’re probably
the ones who killed Mu Dan.

21:23.031 --> 21:26.034
Opportunities to gain
that much Tao don’t come often.

21:26.118 --> 21:27.202
Therefore,

21:27.286 --> 21:30.706
we will now conduct the Rite of Abstaining
and Sustaining Life.

21:30.789 --> 21:32.958
Capture the humans.

21:33.041 --> 21:36.545
What about the new arrivals, brother?

21:36.628 --> 21:38.797
Leave them to the Doshi.

21:38.880 --> 21:41.300
They're heading here.

21:41.383 --> 21:44.177
No need to hunt them ourselves.

21:44.261 --> 21:46.305
I’ll tell you the timing.

21:47.431 --> 21:48.432
Are you sure?

21:49.349 --> 21:52.477
I told you, didn't I? I can feel it.

21:52.561 --> 21:54.688
However, I have one condition.

21:56.023 --> 21:57.441
Fine.

21:59.901 --> 22:00.944
That’s why

22:01.528 --> 22:04.197
I was waiting here for you...

22:05.657 --> 22:08.452
You're offerings for the Rite
of Abstaining and Sustaining Life.

22:09.453 --> 22:10.579
The rite of...

22:10.662 --> 22:12.664
High-quality Tao,

22:12.748 --> 22:16.460
wood, fire, earth, metal,
water, all gathered,

22:16.543 --> 22:18.837
to be offered to the Master.

22:18.920 --> 22:22.841
In other words, you are the offerings.

22:27.429 --> 22:31.433
By now, your comrades
have likely been split up.

22:35.187 --> 22:38.607
The Tensen will personally capture them.

22:42.360 --> 22:44.863
One by one.

22:44.946 --> 22:46.782
And process them carefully.

22:47.449 --> 22:50.869
That is the Rite of Abstaining
and Sustaining Life.

22:50.952 --> 22:54.122
You must have come up with some plan,

22:54.206 --> 22:55.874
but it was all for nothing.

22:57.209 --> 23:00.003
Do not engage the Tensen.

23:00.087 --> 23:02.255
If you do, the plan fails.

23:02.339 --> 23:03.632
Gabimaru...

23:07.219 --> 23:08.595
It's over.

24:23.503 --> 24:25.881
Subtitle translation by: Maslin Friedman
